Looking to trade my T206 commons for a few low grade HOF’ers if possible. Raw or SGC would be preferred. 

Happy to send clearer pictures of individual cards. Most are low grade, piedmont and sweet cap backs.

Let me know if there is any interest!

Matt Galvin

BUMP, possible deal pending on a few, but definitely interested in trading if anyone is willing.

Would be a great time to add multiple commons to your Monster set by trading instead of making purchases over the holiday season!

Matt Galvin
